     H            Y/                                    1
     FGDIPW25 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     F                                              KINFDS INFDS
     FGDIPL25 UF  E           K        DISK                      A
     FGCQPL12 IF  E           K        DISK
     E****************************************************************
     E                    MSG     1  30 60               d[ｰ xｮﾈｰﾆﾞ
     I****************************************************************
     IINFDS       DS
     I                                    B 378 3790POS
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80IKINP
     I                                        1   40IKINPY
     I                                        5   60IKINPM
     I                                        7   80IKINPD
      *ASJ ORDER RECEIVED DATE
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80IKRECV
     I                                        1   40IKJYYY
     I                                        5   60IKJYMM
     I                                        7   80IKJYDD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80D1RECV
     I                                        1   40D1JYYY
     I                                        5   60D1JYMM
     I                                        7   80D1JYDD
      *ASJ PROCESSING DATE
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80IKASJ
     I                                        1   40IKASJY
     I                                        5   60IKASJM
     I                                        7   80IKASJD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80D1ASJ
     I                                        1   40D1ASJY
     I                                        5   60D1ASJM
     I                                        7   80D1ASJD
      *DEPARTURE JP PORT DATE
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80IKSKO
     I                                        1   40IKSKOY
     I                                        5   60IKSKOM
     I                                        7   80IKSKOD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80D1SKO
     I                                        1   40D1SKOY
     I                                        5   60D1SKOM
     I                                        7   80D1SKOD
      *CALCULATION ARRIVAL KSCHEDULE
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80IKTOY
     I                                        1   40IKTOYY
     I                                        5   60IKTOYM
     I                                        7   80IKTOYD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80D1TOY
     I                                        1   40D1TOYY
     I                                        5   60D1TOYM
     I                                        7   80D1TOYD
     I*
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80A2GSHZ
     I                                        1   40A2GSYY
     I                                        5   60A2GSMM
     I                                        7   80A2GSDD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80IKSKHZ
     I                                        1   40IKSKYY
     I                                        5   60IKSKMM
     I                                        7   80IKSKDD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80IKKOHZ
     I                                        1   40IKKOYY
     I                                        5   60IKKOMM
     I                                        7   80IKKODD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   40IKKOTM
     I                                        1   20IKKOHH
     I                                        3   40IKKOSS
     I            DS
     I                                        1   60@@TIME
     I                                        1   40@TIME
     C****************************************************************
     C* MAIN
     C****************************************************************
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PPUSER 10
     C*
     C           KEY01     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           D1ODER
     C                     KFLD           D1ITEM
     C                     KFLD           D1IKBN
     C                     KFLD           D1PARE
     C                     KFLD           D1BXNO
     C           KEY02     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           D2KAT1
     C                     KFLD           D2KAT2
     C                     KFLD           D2KAT3
     C*================================================================
     C                     MOVE '#INIT   '@STEP   8
     C*
     C           @STEP     DOUEQ'#END    '
     C           @STEP     CASEQ'#INIT   '#INIT
     C           @STEP     CASEQ'#DSP1   '#DSP1
     C           @STEP     CASEQ'#CHK1   '#CHK1
     C           @STEP     CASEQ'#DSP2   '#DSP2
     C           @STEP     CASEQ'#CHK2   '#CHK2
     C           @STEP     CASEQ'#CHK2U  '#CHK2
     C           @STEP     CASEQ'#UPD    '#UPD
     C                     ENDCS
     C                     ENDDO
     C*
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C*================================================================
     C*  INIT
     C*================================================================
     C           #INIT     BEGSR
     C                     MOVEA*ALL'0'   *IN
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D1KBN
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1ODER
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1ITEM
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1IKBN
 %001C                     MOVE *BLANK    D1PARE
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1BXNO
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D1INVO
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1RECV
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1ASJ
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1SKO
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1TOY
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D1ERR
     C*
     C                     MOVE '#DSP1   '@STEP
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
     C*================================================================
     C*  DSP1
     C*================================================================
     C           #DSP1     BEGSR
     C                     EXFMTDSP01
     C                     MOVE '#CHK1   '@STEP
     C* < F1=ON >
     C           *INKA     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE '#END    '@STEP
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDSR
     C*================================================================
     C*  CHK1
     C*================================================================
     C           #CHK1     BEGSR
     C                     MOVEA'00000000'*IN,11           11 - 18
     C                     MOVEA'00'      *IN,19           19 - 20
     C                     SETOF                     99
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D1ERR
     C*  UPDATE
     C           D1KBN     IFNE '0'
     C           D1KBN     ANDNE'2'
      *                         ..KOUSINN KUBUNN ERR..
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,1     D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     1199
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           D1ODER    IFEQ 0
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,5     D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     1299
     C                     ENDIF
     C           D1ITEM    IFEQ 0
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,6     D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     1399
     C                     ENDIF
 %001C           D1PARE    IFEQ *BLANK
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,7     D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     1499
     C                     ENDIF
     C           D1BXNO    IFEQ 0
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,8     D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     1599
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           KEY01     CHAINGDIPL25             N90
S1   C           *IN90     IFEQ *ON
 S2  C           D1KBN     IFEQ '0'                        CANCEL
      *                         ..MITOUROKU         ..
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,2     D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     121314
     C  N99                SETON                     1599
 X2  C                     ELSE
     C                     CLEARGDIPL251
 E2  C                     ENDIF
X1   C                     ELSE
 S2  C           IKSKJY    IFEQ 'D'                        DELETE CODE
     C           IKSKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
  S3 C           D1KBN     IFEQ '2'                        ADD
     C                     CLEARGDIPL251
  E3 C                     ENDIF
  S3 C           D1KBN     IFEQ '0'                        CANCEL
      *                         ..SAKUJYO ZUMI..
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,3     D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     121314
     C  N99                SETON                     1599
  E3 C                     ENDIF
 X2  C                     ELSE
  S3 C           D1KBN     IFEQ '2'                        ADD
      *                         ..TOUROKU ZUMI      ..
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,4     D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     1199
  E3 C                     ENDIF
 E2  C                     ENDIF
E1   C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C*  TUIKA JI NO CHECK
     C*
S1   C           D1KBN     IFEQ '2'                        ADD
      *                         ..MINYUURYOKU ..
 S2  C           D1INVO    IFEQ *BLANK
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,9     D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     1699
 E2  C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           D1RECV    IFEQ 0
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,11    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     1799
     C                     ELSE
     C           D1JYYY    IFLT 2000
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,10    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     1799
     C                     ENDIF
     C           D1JYMM    IFLE 0
     C           D1JYMM    ORGT 12
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,10    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     1799
     C                     ENDIF
     C           D1JYDD    IFLE 0
     C           D1JYDD    ORGT 31
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,10    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     1799
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           D1ASJ     IFEQ 0
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,12    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     1899
     C                     ELSE
     C           D1ASJY    IFLT 2000
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,10    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     1899
     C                     ENDIF
     C           D1ASJM    IFLE 0
     C           D1ASJM    ORGT 12
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,10    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     1899
     C                     ENDIF
     C           D1ASJD    IFLE 0
     C           D1ASJD    ORGT 31
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,10    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     1899
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           D1SKO     IFEQ 0
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,13    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     1999
     C                     ELSE
     C           D1SKOY    IFLT 2000
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,10    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     1999
     C                     ENDIF
     C           D1SKOM    IFLE 0
     C           D1SKOM    ORGT 12
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,10    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     1999
     C                     ENDIF
     C           D1SKOD    IFLE 0
     C           D1SKOD    ORGT 31
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,10    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     1999
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           D1TOY     IFEQ 0
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,14    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     2099
     C                     ELSE
     C           D1TOYY    IFLT 2000
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,10    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     2099
     C                     ENDIF
     C           D1TOYM    IFLE 0
     C           D1TOYM    ORGT 12
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,10    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     2099
     C                     ENDIF
     C           D1TOYD    IFLE 0
     C           D1TOYD    ORGT 31
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,10    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     2099
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
E1   C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *OFF
     C           D1KBN     IFEQ '0'                        CANCEL
     C                     SETON                     30
     C                     MOVELIKINVO    D1INVO
     C                     Z-ADDIKRECV    D1RECV
     C                     Z-ADDIKASJ     D1ASJ
     C                     Z-ADDIKSKO     D1SKO
     C                     Z-ADDIKTOY     D1TOY
     C                     MOVELIKKAT1    D2KAT1
     C                     MOVELIKKAT2    D2KAT2
     C                     MOVELIKKAT3    D2KAT3
     C                     MOVELIKKAT4    D2KAT4
     C                     Z-ADDIKSYOS    D2SYOS
     C                     Z-ADDIKSBOX    D2SBOX
     C                     Z-ADDIKTANK    D2TANK
     C                     MOVELIKHANY    D2HANY
     C                     ELSE
     C                     SETOF                     30
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D2KAT1
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D2KAT2
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D2KAT3
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D2KAT4
     C                     Z-ADD0         D2SYOS
     C                     Z-ADD0         D2SBOX
     C                     Z-ADD0         D2TANK
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D2HANY
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     MOVE '#DSP2   '@STEP
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE '#DSP1   '@STEP
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDSR
     C*================================================================
     C*  DSP2
     C*================================================================
     C           #DSP2     BEGSR
     C                     EXFMTDSP02
     C                     MOVE '#CHK2   '@STEP
     C* < F3=ON >
     C           *INKC     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVEA*ALL'0'   *IN
     C                     MOVE '#DSP1   '@STEP
     C                     ENDIF
     C* < F5=ON >
     C           *INKE     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE '#CHK2U  '@STEP
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDSR
     C*================================================================
     C*================================================================
     C*  CHK2
     C*================================================================
     C           #CHK2     BEGSR
     C                     MOVEA'00000000'*IN,21           21 - 28
     C                     SETOF                     99
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D1ERR
     C*
     C           D2KAT1    IFEQ *BLANK
     C           D2KAT2    ANDEQ*BLANK
     C           D2KAT3    ANDEQ*BLANK
     C           D2KAT4    ANDEQ*BLANK
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,15    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     2199
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     SETOF                     50
     C           KEY02     CHAINGCQPL121             50
     C           *IN50     IFEQ '0'
     C           T6SKJY    ANDEQ'D'
     C           T6SKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     SETON                     50
     C                     END
     C           *IN50     IFEQ '1'
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,16    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     2199
     C                     ENDIF
     C**
     C           D2SYOS    IFEQ 0
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,17    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     2299
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           D2SBOX    IFEQ 0
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,18    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     2399
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           D2TANK    IFEQ 0
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,19    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     2499
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           D2HANY    IFEQ *BLANK
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,20    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     2599
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           D2HANY    IFEQ 'S'
     C           D2HANY    OREQ 'A'
     C                     ELSE
     C  N99                MOVELMSG,21    D1ERR
     C  N99                SETON                     2599
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *OFF
     C           @STEP     ANDEQ'#CHK2U  '
     C                     MOVE '#UPD    '@STEP
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE '#DSP2   '@STEP
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
     C*================================================================
     C*  UPD
     C*================================================================
     C           #UPD      BEGSR
     C           KEY01     CHAINGDIPL25              90
     C           *IN90     IFEQ *OFF
     C           D1KBN     IFEQ '0'                        CANCEL
     C                     TIME           @@TIME
     C                     MOVE 'D'       IKSKJY
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     IKSKHZ
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     IKKOHZ
     C                     Z-ADD@TIME     IKKOTM
     C                     MOVE PPUSER    IKKOME
     C                     UPDATGDIPL251
     C                     ENDIF
     C           D1KBN     IFEQ '2'                        ADD
     C                     TIME           @@TIME
     C                     MOVE ' '       IKSKJY
     C                     Z-ADD0         IKSKHZ
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     IKKOHZ
     C                     Z-ADD@TIME     IKKOTM
     C                     MOVE PPUSER    IKKOME
     C                     EXSR #MOVE
     C                     UPDATGDIPL251
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ELSE
     C           D1KBN     IFEQ '2'                        ADD
     C                     TIME           @@TIME
     C                     MOVE ' '       IKSKJY
     C                     Z-ADD0         IKSKHZ
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     IKKOHZ
     C                     Z-ADD@TIME     IKKOTM
     C                     MOVE PPUSER    IKKOME
     C*
     C                     EXSR #MOVE
     C                     WRITEGDIPL251
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           D1KBN     IFEQ '0'                        CANCEL
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D1INVO
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1RECV
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1ASJ
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1SKO
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1TOY
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D1KBN
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1ODER
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1ITEM
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1IKBN
 %001C                     MOVE *BLANK    D1PARE
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1BXNO
     C                     MOVEA*ALL'0'   *IN
     C                     MOVE '#DSP1   '@STEP
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
     C*================================================================
     C           #MOVE     BEGSR
     C                     MOVE D1INVO    IKINVO
     C                     Z-ADDD1ODER    IKODER
     C                     Z-ADDD1ITEM    IKITEM
     C                     Z-ADDD1IKBN    IKIKBN
 %001C                     MOVE D1PARE    IKPARE
     C                     Z-ADDD1BXNO    IKBXNO
     C                     MOVELD2KAT1    IKKAT1
     C                     MOVELD2KAT2    IKKAT2
     C                     MOVELD2KAT3    IKKAT3
     C                     MOVELD2KAT4    IKKAT4
     C                     Z-ADDD2SYOS    IKSYOS
     C                     Z-ADDD2SBOX    IKSBOX
     C           D2SYOS    MULT D2SBOX    IKSURY
     C                     Z-ADDD2TANK    IKTANK
     C                     MOVELD2HANY    IKHANY
     C                     Z-ADDD1RECV    IKRECV
     C                     Z-ADDD1ASJ     IKASJ
     C                     Z-ADDD1SKO     IKSKO
     C                     Z-ADDD1TOY     IKTOY
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     IKINP
     C                     Z-ADD0         IKNYUY
     C                     Z-ADD0         IKNYUM
     C                     Z-ADD0         IKNYUD
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    IKNYUK
     C                     ENDSR
     C*================================================================
**  MSG (mｰﾎﾞﾓ ﾃx]n)
E-01 MUST INPUT < 0.2 > FOR UPDATE INSTRUCTION
E-02 ITEM NO NOT FOUND IN ORDER SHEET.
E-03 THIS ITEM NO IS ALREADY CANCEL.
E-04 THIS ITEM NO IS ALREADY FINISH.
E-05 INPUT ORDER NO.
E-06 INPUT ITEM NO.
E-07 INPUT PALLETE NO.
E-08 INPUT SN-BOX NO.
E-09 INPUT INVOICE NO.
E-10 INCORRECT DATE.
E-11 INPUT ORDER RECEIVED DATE.
E-12 INPUT ASJ PROCESSING DATE.
E-13 INPUT DEPARTURE JP PORT DATE.
E-14 INPUT CALCULATION ARRIVAL KSCHEDULE DATE.
E-15 INPUT DIE CODE.
E-16 DIE CODE NOT FOUND IN DIE M/F.
E-17 INPUT QTY/BOX
E-18 INPUT BOX
E-19 INPUT UNIT PRICE
E-20 INPUT CARRY CODE
E-21 CARRY CODE IS WRONG
